                <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.373 3.373 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
                <h3>AI 智能投研分析</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4 text-slate-300">输入一家公司（或行业类型），让 AI 为您生成一份专业的“A+H”上市战略分析报告。</p>
